<H1><A NAME="SECTION00030000000000000000">
Comparison Theorems</A>
</H1>

<P>
Remember the definition of the <EM>complement</EM>

<P>
<BR><P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
{U}^{\bot}:=\{f \in {W}^*={\rm Hom}_{R}{(W,R)}| \; f(u)=0 \; \, \forall u \in U\}
