<P>
Turning to our special situation we first note that 
<!-- MATH
 $tr(b[x,a])=tr(x[a,b])$
 -->
<IMG
 WIDTH="185" HEIGHT="37" ALIGN="MIDDLE" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img64.png"
