<A HREF="node3.html#duales_Komplement">3.1</A> we have

<P>
<BR><P></P>
<DIV ALIGN="CENTER">
<!-- MATH
 \begin{displaymath}
K(A)\subseteq{\rm Ev}_{{{\cal E}}^*}^{-1}({{K(A)}^{\bot}}^{\bot})=
{\rm Ev}_{{{\cal E}}^*}^{-1}({\rm Ev}_{{{\cal E}}^*}({C(A)}^{\bot}))= {C(A)}^{\bot}
