...{\cal E}}^*}({C(A)}^{\bot}))= {C(A)}^{\bot}
={\rm ker}({J}^*). \end{displaymath}">
</DIV>
<BR CLEAR="ALL">
<P></P>

<P>
Therefore <IMG
 WIDTH="24" HEIGHT="18" ALIGN="BOTTOM" BORDER="0"
 SRC="img98.png"
 ALT="${J}^*$"> factors to an <IMG
 WIDTH="19" HEIGHT="18" ALIGN="BOTTOM" BORDER="0"
