This immediately implies

<P>
<P>
<DIV><A NAME="schwaches_Kriterium"><B>Corollary  3.5</B></A> (Criterion of torsion freeness)  &nbsp; 
The following statements are equivalent:
<DL COMPACT>
<DT>(a)</DT>
<DD><IMG
